{"tid":1741420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RB加固, 唔使用劍既, 用快乾英泥就得la","createTime":"2019-11-20T10:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:37:20.000Z","uid":319687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd39c544dc78ad27bd7fcbdfb6303421623c98f5","tid":1741420,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dX0vwYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdX0vwYb.jpg&h=c9523048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n固定磚做RB, 你用1分鐘set, 人地要打炮 / 成個鐘咁鏟先清到<br />\n有一款叫快乾英泥, 就咁溝水, 唔使溝沙, <br />\n溝完水之後10分鐘內要用<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">半個鐘內乾</span></span></strong>, 硬度同普通英泥溝沙一樣咁硬<br />\n乾佐之後要用打炮槍先打得爛<br />\n就咁用手腳係整唔走<br />\n25KG 120蚊到, <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">{除佐快乾泥外, 仲有一支叫做快乾水, 普通英泥溝完沙再溝快乾水都有相同效果}</span></strong><br />\n唔係間間賣英泥既地方都有, 防水鋪有售<br />\n同埋好多相關既鋪頭都係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></strong>,<br />\n買果陣淋定點解要買, 佢會逗人<br />\n如屋企塊磚爛佐, 要貼返<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Fact Checked 以下鋪頭有售</span></strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qCBsuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qCBsuS.png&h=62f4ca4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6M27uW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6M27uW.png&h=cbb13ef5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7c3761e203ad9cc8394f7482435f8da1d96e7b7","tid":1741420,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"邊有咗多水 消防喉？"},{"pid":"6072b5f080f0fb20bc9201bcdad333410848416a","tid":1741420,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"送錢畀藍絲賺，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg